msgctxt "sn46.55:22.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yenekadā dīgharattaṃ asajjhāyakatāpi mantā paṭibhanti, pageva sajjhāyakatā. "
msgstr "This is the cause, brahmin, this is the reason why sometimes even hymns that are long-unpracticed do spring to mind, let alone those that are practiced. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc23
msgctxt "sn46.55:23.1"
msgid "Sattime, brāhmaṇa, bojjhaṅgā anāvaraṇā anīvaraṇā cetaso anupakkilesā bhāvitā bahulīkatā vijjāvimuttiphalasacchikiriyāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "These seven awakening factors are not obstacles, hindrances, or corruptions of the mind. When developed and cultivated they lead to the realization of the fruit of knowledge and freedom. "

msgctxt "sn46.55:23.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.55:23.3"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo kho, brāhmaṇa, anāvaraṇo anīvaraṇo cetaso anupakkileso bhāvito bahulīkato vijjāvimuttiphalasacchikiriyāya saṃvattati … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo kho, brāhmaṇa, anāvaraṇo anīvaraṇo cetaso anupakkileso bhāvito bahulīkato vijjāvimuttiphalasacchikiriyāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.55:23.4"
msgid "Ime kho, brāhmaṇa, satta bojjhaṅgā anāvaraṇā anīvaraṇā cetaso anupakkilesā bhāvitā bahulīkatā vijjāvimuttiphalasacchikiriyāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "These seven awakening factors are not obstacles, hindrances, or corruptions of the mind. When developed and cultivated they lead to the realization of the fruit of knowledge and freedom.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc24
msgctxt "sn46.55:24.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, saṅgāravo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, Saṅgārava said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn46.55:24.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! … "

msgctxt "sn46.55:24.3"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.55:24.4"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

